data.description: WOW! Beautiful home ready for its new owner! To start from the top.. As you walk in you will find a large entry way, along with a formal dining that could easily be turned into an office! Continue on and you'll see the kitchen opened up to the living room, fireplace and 2nd dining area. Going into the Master there will be a beautiful accent wall, then the jetted garden tub and last but definitely not least... The OVERSIZED master closet!! You will have absolutely no issues storing all of your clothing in this closet! Moving on to the second story.. As you approach the top of the stairs, you'll be greeted by the large 2nd living area that would also make a great game or theatre room. You will then finish out the second story by the 3 secondary bedrooms along with 1 full bathroom!! Do you like privacy? Let's not forget the backyard has an 8ft privacy fence! This home also comes with a new water heater that has only been in use for a month! Get your showing scheduled now!!
